A plugin is a prepackaged bundle that can combine:

- 1 MCP connector
- 2 skills
- 1 slash command
- 1 subagent

So in JSON, it can look like this:

```json
{
  "plugin": {
    "name": "sample-plugin",
    "mcp_connectors": [
      {
        "name": "sample-mcp",
        "type": "connector"
      }
    ],
    "skills": [
      {
        "name": "skill-1",
        "type": "skill"
      },
      {
        "name": "skill-2",
        "type": "skill"
      }
    ],
    "slash_commands": [
      {
        "name": "/sample-command",
        "type": "slash_command"
      }
    ],
    "subagents": [
      {
        "name": "sample-subagent",
        "type": "subagent"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

